dct_description_sm: From: From Atlas universel de geographie physique, politique, statistique et minéralogique, sur l'echelle de 1:1641836 ... / dressé par Ph. Vandermaelen. Bruxelles : [Ph. Vandermaelen], 1827. Relief shown by landform drawings. Covers also Aruba, Bonaire, and the southernmost parts of the Dominican Republic and Puerto Rico, and parts of Falcón State, Venezuela and La Guajira Department, Colombia. Includes text: Republique d'Haïti / redigée par A. Delavault.
